enb_long_title: Eleventh Session of The INC for the Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
sentences: In Rules 9, 10 and 11, the word 'draft' was added before 'provisional agenda.
' The Russian Federation proposed deleting 'draft' from Rules 10 and 11 and reformulating Rule 9: 'In agreement with the President, the secretariat shall draft the provisional agenda of each session.
In Rule 12, delegates accepted the language adapted from the Biodiversity Convention Rules of Procedure.
